    <item>
      <title>泰国经济增长 3%，出口和刺激措施超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/thai-economy-grows-3-beating-estimates-on-exports-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国第三季度经济增长速度快于预期，出口改善和政府支出抵消了私人消费放缓的影响，政府计划采取进一步刺激措施以维持增长势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/thai-economy-grows-3-beating-estimates-on-exports-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 02:36:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛表示，随着各国央行购买黄金、美联储在 25 年降息，黄金将大行其道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/goldman-says-go-for-gold-as-central-banks-buy-fed-cuts-in-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团表示，受央行购买和美国降息推动，金价明年将上涨至创纪录水平。高盛将金价列为 2025 年最热门大宗商品交易之一，并表示在唐纳德·特朗普担任总统期间，金价可能延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/goldman-says-go-for-gold-as-central-banks-buy-fed-cuts-in-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 02:32:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿里巴巴将发行债券偿还债务并回购股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/alibaba-to-offer-notes-for-debt-repayment-share-repurchases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继今年早些时候发行创纪录的可转换债券后，阿里巴巴集团控股有限公司已聘请银行出售美元和人民币债券，这些债券将用于偿还海外债务和回购股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/alibaba-to-offer-notes-for-debt-repayment-share-repurchases</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 01:19:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
